<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM6.9">
<l>varicilai vāṇmukat teṉṉaimār tāmvantiṭ</l>
<l>ṭerimukam pārit teṉṉaimuṉ ṉēniṟutti</l>
<l>yarimuka ṉaccutaṉ kaimmēleṉ kaivaittup</l>
<l>porimukan taṭṭak kaṉākkaṇṭēṉ tōḻīnāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O friend! I dreamt that my brothers with lustrous faces</l>
<l>and striped bow[-like eyebrows] came, fostered the sacrificial fire,</l>
<l>made me stand before [it],</l>
<l>placed my hand upon the lion-faced Acyuta’s hand,</l>
<l>took up puffed rice [and] scattered [it in our hands].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
